msgid "**Value raster layer**"
msgstr "**Waardenrasterlaag**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:20
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:432
